<div class="hero">
	<div class="hero-body">
		<h1>Calculator</h1>
		<p>Use the options below to showcase how much money you will earn. The days option will allow you to see how much money you have earned over your chosen number of days and when you will hit your limit depending on your VIP level. The Amount option will show you the date that you will reach your specified amount.</p>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="container">
    <div class="calculator">
        <div class="calculator-form">
			<div class="tabs">
				<ul>
					<li><a href="#" data-target="days" class="active">Days</a></li>
					<li><a href="#" data-target="balance">Balance</a></li>
				</ul>
				<div id="tab-indicator"></div>
			</div>    
			
			<div class="content">
				<div id="days">
					{% include "days-form.njk" %}
				</div>

				<div id="balance" class="hidden">
					{% include "balance-form.njk" %}
				</div>
			</div>
        </div>

        <div class="calculator-table">
			<div class="buttons">
				<button class="clear hiden">Clear Table</button>
				<button id="downloadExcel" class="disabled hiden">Export to Excel</button>
				<button id="downloadExcelRows" class="disabled hiden">Export Highlights</button>
				<button id="remove-highlights" class="disabled hiden">Clear highlights</button>
			</div>

			<table class="hiden">
				<thead>
					<tr>
						<th>Day</th>
						<th>Daily</th>
						<th>Acc Earnings</th>
						<th>Percentage</th>
						<th>Balance</th>
					</tr>
				</thead>
